      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 08:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Finma 总裁希望避免瑞银在资本缓冲争论中“争执不休”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/finma-chief-says-he-s-not-looking-for-feud-in-ubs-capital-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士银行业监管机构负责人表示，他并不打算与瑞银集团（UBS Group AG）产生“争执”，同时表示他将继续推动对瑞士最大银行提高资本要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/finma-chief-says-he-s-not-looking-for-feud-in-ubs-capital-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 08:31:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
