      <title>空客正就向中国出售 100 多架宽体飞机进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/airbus-in-talks-to-sell-more-than-100-widebody-jets-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[空中客车公司正在就向中国出售 A330neo 飞机进行谈判，自上个月习近平主席访问法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙以来，谈判势头强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/airbus-in-talks-to-sell-more-than-100-widebody-jets-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 05:49:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
